{"tid":2478684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁淳修出殯 同事列隊致敬高喊：任務結束","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T10:35:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7afb5fec18a414c7cf88f3ebcbe8412f57db755e","tid":2478684,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210407/ZD3ORUOKIBAFJPWQN34HCVSOKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210407%2FZD3ORUOKIBAFJPWQN34HCVSOKY%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=28ea0a80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210407%2FZD3ORUOKIBAFJPWQN34HCVSOKY%2F&h=74c72fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210407/ZD3ORUOKIBAFJPWQN34HCVSOKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n袁淳修出殯 同事列隊致敬高喊：任務結束<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7BUqyUegQm-_7FqHAaAYBgmGJUs=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AFN3UFGOKBHVFJ5QIRIMBWUXMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7BUqyUegQm-_7FqHAaAYBgmGJUs%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAFN3UFGOKBHVFJ5QIRIMBWUXMQ.jpg&h=006943c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■袁淳修的骨灰昨由家屬和親友帶返台中。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n任務結束！台鐵職員與鐵路警察列隊呼喊，劃破寧靜哀戚，更顯悲壯。上周五台鐵太魯閣號事故，司機袁淳修不幸殉職，昨日由親友抱住其骨灰上禮車，正式離開他用生命守護的鐵路世界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林佳龍哽咽 「感謝守護乘客」<br />\n<br />\n用生命最後四秒全力煞車，袁淳修為保護全車旅客安全而殉職。昨日早上，袁淳修的葬禮在花蓮殯儀館舉行，交通部長林佳龍到場致意，悼念時數度哽咽，「淳修任務結束，感謝你守護乘客到最後一刻」，隨後他轉身與家屬。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨天中午，台灣衞福部的賑災專線收到兩億新台幣（約5,470萬港元）善款，當局將成立捐款管理及監督委員會審核。港鐵工會「港鐵新動力」在Facebook宣佈，與台灣鐵路產。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"6131f4583996779137b66abab81f6a5cea030410","tid":2478684,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"0f9a12670b4ccb6278bdc3febee4208479d80746","tid":2478684,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6131f4583996779137b66abab81f6a5cea030410","tid":2478684,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"RIP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc13a6e3f263b538a5cd203e5f38fa02f8d42f13","tid":2478684,"uid":276693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"dc42d18e64d97cbd0679f4162473ba377194767d","tid":2478684,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔想再見到放負L計秒數<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2105c4158f872977c9229489d8634e191901ebe","tid":2478684,"uid":217336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcafd37a447a474cdbf5d2c154e15593779bc71","tid":2478684,"uid":395358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔係玩電話可能唔使死咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAnyways rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}